00:01:11.360 --> 00:01:12.200
In the end,

00:01:12.440 --> 00:01:13.880
is this world worse than a dog,

00:01:14.200 --> 00:01:15.800
or is the Prefect worse than a dog?

00:01:17.240 --> 00:01:18.000
Who are you?

00:01:18.480 --> 00:01:20.400
How dare you break into the Prefect's residence?

00:01:21.800 --> 00:01:23.120
Shouldn't you first ask me

00:01:23.280 --> 00:01:24.360
how I got in?

00:01:25.160 --> 00:01:26.120
Oh, you—

00:01:27.080 --> 00:01:28.600
How did you get in?

00:01:29.360 --> 00:01:30.080
Your Excellency,

00:01:30.480 --> 00:01:32.360
surely you don't think this residence

00:01:32.600 --> 00:01:34.280
truly belongs to you?

00:01:34.480 --> 00:01:35.760
Just give someone a bit of silver,

00:01:35.760 --> 00:01:36.840
and they'll let me pass.

00:01:37.280 --> 00:01:37.880
Nonsense!

00:01:39.560 --> 00:01:40.680
Li Wenshun.

00:01:41.400 --> 00:01:42.360
Courtesy name: Hongzhi.

00:01:42.600 --> 00:01:43.440
From the capital.

00:01:43.520 --> 00:01:45.200
Transferred to Nan County as Prefect.

00:01:45.480 --> 00:01:46.520
Been in office for over a year.

00:01:46.720 --> 00:01:47.840
Accomplished nothing.

00:01:47.960 --> 00:01:48.960
Not only sidelined,

00:01:49.320 --> 00:01:50.760
even that mere Wang Lie

00:01:50.800 --> 00:01:53.240
dares to treat the Prefect as nothing.

00:01:53.400 --> 00:01:55.080
How pitiful.

00:01:55.760 --> 00:01:56.320
Your Excellency,

00:01:56.800 --> 00:01:57.360
why not

00:01:57.880 --> 00:01:58.680
sit down and talk?

00:02:06.560 --> 00:02:07.120
You—

00:02:08.240 --> 00:02:09.360
Who are you, really?

00:02:19.520 --> 00:02:20.280
Li Ling.

00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:21.320
Oh?

00:02:21.680 --> 00:02:23.000
The Prefect recognizes me.

00:02:24.600 --> 00:02:27.000
Your likeness is on the wanted notice.

00:02:27.360 --> 00:02:29.200
How could I not know you?

00:02:30.360 --> 00:02:31.720
As the Prefect,

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:34.600
you can remember the faces on wanted notices.

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:37.160
Shows you're a diligent official.

00:02:37.560 --> 00:02:38.800
But why does an official,

00:02:39.040 --> 00:02:40.280
even a good one,

00:02:40.680 --> 00:02:42.440
end up in such a state?

00:02:43.720 --> 00:02:44.560
What do you know?

00:02:45.160 --> 00:02:45.680
Hmm.

00:02:46.520 --> 00:02:47.760
Those officials,

00:02:48.160 --> 00:02:50.160
all collude together.

00:02:50.920 --> 00:02:51.920
Here in Nan County,

00:02:52.320 --> 00:02:55.160
there's drought or flooding every few days.

00:02:55.520 --> 00:02:58.040
Even with Herculean ability,

00:02:58.040 --> 00:02:59.440
what could I possibly do?

00:03:01.400 --> 00:03:03.200
To raise funds for disaster relief,

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:05.680
I have no choice but to turn to these merchants.

00:03:06.040 --> 00:03:08.040
But their money

00:03:08.600 --> 00:03:10.800
is poison that eats away at the bones.

00:03:10.960 --> 00:03:12.840
So you just sit here complaining,

00:03:12.840 --> 00:03:13.720
feeling sorry for yourself.

00:03:13.920 --> 00:03:14.720
Acting like this,

00:03:14.720 --> 00:03:15.760
do you still call yourself a true man?

00:03:15.960 --> 00:03:16.680
How dare you!

00:03:16.680 --> 00:03:19.040
Have you considered why you've ended up like this?

00:03:19.320 --> 00:03:20.840
Why do the rivers always break their banks?

00:03:21.080 --> 00:03:22.640
Why is there never enough food?

00:03:22.880 --> 00:03:24.720
Why are the people always displaced?

00:03:24.920 --> 00:03:25.840
And Wang Lie—

00:03:26.320 --> 00:03:28.080
