00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:39.040
even your head won't be safe.

00:03:40.520 --> 00:03:42.040
Even your family

00:03:42.800 --> 00:03:44.560
will surely be implicated.

00:03:45.120 --> 00:03:45.760
When that time comes,

00:03:46.160 --> 00:03:47.680
you'll be cursed by thousands,

00:03:48.240 --> 00:03:49.840
branded as a corrupt official.

00:03:52.880 --> 00:03:53.840
You came to see me

00:03:54.480 --> 00:03:55.920
just to say all this?

00:03:57.560 --> 00:03:58.120
Your Excellency,

00:03:58.640 --> 00:03:59.240
I came

00:03:59.720 --> 00:04:00.520
to help you.

00:04:01.640 --> 00:04:02.240
You—

00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:03.520
help me?

00:04:05.120 --> 00:04:06.080
How will you help me?

00:04:06.960 --> 00:04:08.320
I want to act first,

00:04:08.480 --> 00:04:10.080
cut off Wang Lie's pearl supply.

00:04:10.960 --> 00:04:12.080
But he controls the grain supply.

00:04:12.600 --> 00:04:13.160
If you,

00:04:13.400 --> 00:04:14.800
don't follow his orders,

00:04:14.960 --> 00:04:16.880
he'll surely use food to threaten you.

00:04:17.320 --> 00:04:17.920
Then,

00:04:18.440 --> 00:04:20.480
we'll see if you dare to join me

00:04:22.240 --> 00:04:23.120
and take a gamble.

00:04:32.200 --> 00:04:32.800
Your Excellency,

00:04:33.080 --> 00:04:34.440
Then I'll take my leave.

00:04:38.320 --> 00:04:39.000
Hey, Li Ling.

00:04:40.240 --> 00:04:41.480
Why are you helping me?

00:04:42.960 --> 00:04:43.560
Your Excellency,

00:04:44.600 --> 00:04:45.640
I'm not helping you.

00:04:46.160 --> 00:04:47.280
I'm helping myself.

00:04:48.320 --> 00:04:49.880
I want you to pave a way for me.

00:04:50.480 --> 00:04:51.200
A way

00:04:51.840 --> 00:04:52.920
that is justifiable

00:04:53.200 --> 00:04:54.200
