00:05:26.040 --> 00:05:26.440
Come, come, come!

00:05:26.440 --> 00:05:26.880
Take a look!

00:05:26.880 --> 00:05:27.560
Come and see!

00:05:28.720 --> 00:05:29.840
Please come inside, sir!

00:05:29.840 --> 00:05:30.680
Take a look!

00:05:36.760 --> 00:05:37.400
In a moment,

00:05:38.080 --> 00:05:39.280
I'll pick out all the shells with pearls.

00:05:39.280 --> 00:05:40.000
