00:05:40.680 --> 00:05:41.880
You take the shells without pearls

00:05:42.400 --> 00:05:43.080
and find someone

00:05:43.280 --> 00:05:45.360
to sell them all to Wang Lie's shop.

00:05:49.880 --> 00:05:50.720
