00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:04.000
But who is the real villain?

00:06:04.200 --> 00:06:06.400
And who will be the one to deal with them?

00:06:07.880 --> 00:06:08.840
Today,

00:06:09.200 --> 00:06:10.680
I'll show Wang Lie

00:06:10.960 --> 00:06:13.640
