00:06:46.080 --> 00:06:47.280
You know nothing.

00:06:47.400 --> 00:06:48.680
Then what use are you to me?

00:06:49.440 --> 00:06:51.840
You made me lose over a hundred thousand coins.

00:06:52.600 --> 00:06:53.680
Take him away.

00:06:54.320 --> 00:06:55.040
