00:08:50.280 --> 00:08:51.080
This is partly my fault.

00:08:51.320 --> 00:08:52.040
I didn’t think it through.

00:08:53.080 --> 00:08:53.760
Hey, Li Ling.

00:08:54.680 --> 00:08:57.480
